                    <span>Not much of a fantasy reader, but, I remember reading this book back when it's first printing came out.  I was in 6th grade, that was...10+ years ago!?!?!  I LOVED this book, and read it twice, cover to cover, before passing it on to my friends.  I'm happy to see it back!  I look foreward to reading it over again, and then sharing with others!  Highly reccomended as abstract teaching for any environmental curriculun involving the teachings of logging practices .vs. Old Growth Forests.  Better for younger audiences, but and adult who hasn't lost their youth or spirit for adventure would enjoy as well!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A simple story...</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
